{"id": "ChIJAV9DxuG5woAR3VNawzv1G4I", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 122, "displayName": {"text": "88PC Cafe", "languageCode": "ko"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJAV9DxuG5woAR3VNawzv1G4I/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201Sk1FRlBZMlJpU1hGVk5uUm1kV2R4TUhSQk9WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "This isn't your high-end PC bang. There was no AC, ping spiked often when playing league, and not your friendliest owner, let alone the price.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This isn't your high-end PC bang. There was no AC, ping spiked often when playing league, and not your friendliest owner, let alone the price.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "tim choi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111563693538935712688/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqD5VFz7QYGsCrq6vbc_5vWmOeYdyw6v-QKcUXPFQntVVTLg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-20T23:16:26.142367313Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201Sk1FRlBZMlJpU1hGVk5uUm1kV2R4TUhSQk9WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT201Sk1FRlBZMlJpU1hGVk5uUm1kV2R4TUhSQk9WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9e1c6435f01:0x821bf53bc35a53dd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJAV9DxuG5woAR3VNawzv1G4I/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVdzVXUnB3RRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 years ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Really clean quick pc's, tell the cashier what number you want to sit at and for how many hours when you go in. They have major games installed and ready and headsets on deck! Docking stars for lack of customer service and explanation given: you kind of fend for yourself. Also the door might be closed due to the AC. Female gamer friendly: the atmosphere was very much people focused on their own monitor, didnt get harrased. IMPORTANT: i don't speak korean so when the headset had a random korean message i guessed my time was almost done and was right, it will boot you automatically so be careful!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really clean quick pc's, tell the cashier what number you want to sit at and for how many hours when you go in. They have major games installed and ready and headsets on deck! Docking stars for lack of customer service and explanation given: you kind of fend for yourself. Also the door might be closed due to the AC. Female gamer friendly: the atmosphere was very much people focused on their own monitor, didnt get harrased. IMPORTANT: i don't speak korean so when the headset had a random korean message i guessed my time was almost done and was right, it will boot you automatically so be careful!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100106885025546132214/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBRY31zgOjX6CU0srvQDjFN0grHaPvy6qvOAwNemIcSbg1fzUw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2019-08-03T03:10:38.992987Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVdzVXUnB3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNVdzVXUnB3RRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9e1c6435f01:0x821bf53bc35a53dd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJAV9DxuG5woAR3VNawzv1G4I/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmdlByY2pBRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It is to me a refreshing and fairly price service. i have access to the folders in my games that enable me to MOD and enjoy the games i like in a way I want. i love this small location and I will be returning as often as i can. I was surprised by the prices and the great internet connection. 10/10 i would\nrecommend.\ni have to say this: the poor reviews are unjustified. that's due to those who expect everything to be catered to them like feeding a hopeless baby who doesn't know how to use any tools at their disposal. People are so harsh to judge because they have expectations that nobody can meet. low 1 stars reviews are from people who are less then smart. this place ia great, you don't speak Korean than use Google translate and be an adult not a crying good for nothing baby.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It is to me a refreshing and fairly price service. i have access to the folders in my games that enable me to MOD and enjoy the games i like in a way I want. i love this small location and I will be returning as often as i can. I was surprised by the prices and the great internet connection. 10/10 i would\nrecommend.\ni have to say this: the poor reviews are unjustified. that's due to those who expect everything to be catered to them like feeding a hopeless baby who doesn't know how to use any tools at their disposal. People are so harsh to judge because they have expectations that nobody can meet. low 1 stars reviews are from people who are less then smart. this place ia great, you don't speak Korean than use Google translate and be an adult not a crying good for nothing baby.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "E S", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104812372584076998439/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhC-6aMhf53kPBNbfvfd2rBrtkmuEmzuYn9GXP6sdpoppP1ac=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2025-02-22T20:02:04.788546Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmdlByY2pBRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmdlByY2pBRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b9e1c6435f01:0x821bf53bc35a53dd"}, {"name": "places/ChIJAV9DxuG5woAR3VNawzv1G4I/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM1Mk11TDNRRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 years ago", "rating": 5, 